body_html: @VolodymyrPavliukevych please feel free to absorb mature components of the first successful TensorFlow Swift language binding acknowledged by google : Perfect TensorFlow, which works well in OS X and Ubuntu and simple easy installation and as well as the runtime downcast compatibility from TensorFlow 1.2 to 1.4. Welcome aboard! The Perfect TensorFlow has already a full testing script with 34 different tests to completely cover the TensorFlow C API. You can take as many as possible, it’s Apache 2.0 open source
